      "end": 254.172,
      "words": [
        "which",
        "they've",
        "been",
        "holding",
        "on",
        "to"
      ]
    },
    {
      "text": "The horse regulates them.",
      "start": 254.412,
      "end": 256.012,
      "words": [
        "The",
        "horse",
        "regulates",
        "them"
      ]
    },
    {
      "text": "Many of the children Claudia works with suffer trauma.",
